'''拉铆螺母'''，俗称'''拉帽'''，是一种[[紧固件|紧固件]]。由于它不需要攻[[螺纹|内螺纹]]，不需要[[焊接|焊接]]螺母、使用气动或手动[[拉铆枪|拉铆枪]]可一次铆固，铆接牢固效率高、使用方便。<ref>{{Citation | last = Smith | first = Carroll | title = Carroll Smith's Nuts, Bolts, Fasteners, and Plumbing Handbook | publisher = MotorBooks/MBI Publishing Company | year = 1990 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=A81HmmRCN7YC | isbn = 0-87938-406-9}}</ref>

为解决金属薄板、薄管焊接[[螺母|螺母]]易熔，攻内螺纹易滑牙等缺点，BF Goodrich 在1930年代发明拉铆螺母，并以RIVNUT®品牌销售。首次应用在飞机[[机翼|机翼]]上的[[除冰套|除冰套]]上<ref>{{Citation | title = RIVNUT® The Original Blind Rivet Nut | publisher = Böllhoff Inc. | year = 2010 | url = https://media.boellhoff.com/files/pdf12/rivnut-us-version-en.pdf | accessdate = 2018-09-25 | archive-date = 2021-01-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210131183559/https://media.boellhoff.com/files/pdf12/rivnut-us-version-en.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>
